Package com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.Command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataManagerAPI
    [Facade Interface] An interface which represents all the methods for frontend objects to interact with the data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddHabitCommand
    [Command Class] AddHabit command subclasses ServerCommmand and represents a command object containing all the data for a new habit to be added for a particular user.
    AddHabitEventCommand
    [Command Class] AddHabitEvent command subclasses ServerCommmand and represents a command object containing all the data for a new habitEvent to be added for a particular user.
    DeleteHabitCommand
    [Command Class] Command to delete a habit from the server Created by Christopher Walter on 2017-11-23.
    DeleteHabitEventCommand
    [Command Class] Command to delete a habit event from the server Created by Christopher Walter on 2017-11-22.
    ServerCommand
    [Command Interface] Command interface for all queue-able commands
    ServerCommandManager
    [Singleton Model Class] A class to manage all the command objects and execute them when a network connection can be established Created by Christopher Walter on 2017-11-03.
    ServerCommandManager.ExecuteAsync
    Static inner class to execute commands on a background thread Loops through all commands in the queue and calls their execute method, upon execution removes them from the queue
    ServerCommandManager.InitializeUserAsync
    Specific Async task for adding a new user
    UpdateUserCommand
    [Command Class] Command to update the user data on the server Created by Christopher Walter on 2017-11-27.
